  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9f7f230a53388af4298629f7332491d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::tutorialPanle
  text: {fileID: 583369830}
  delay: 0.02
  pages:
  - 'we ran out of time for a proper introduction, so you get a text explaination
    instead.


'
  - 'The loop is simple.


    1. Go to the shop above to buy drug ingredients.

    2.
    Go back home and [insert way to make drugs].

    3. Hide drugs inside your house
    until the timer runs out.

    4. Wait for the police to search your house.

    5.
    Repeat until you die =)'
  - 'Movment


    Walking - WASD

    Throwing - LMB

    Turning Camera - Q/E


    pretty
    much it.'
